  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Sorcerer Bloodline Power</strong><br/><br/><p>At 9th level, swarms no longer see you as prey. You can walk among swarms without fear of being harmed by them at all, and by taking a standard action to mentally command a swarm in which you stand, you can direct that swarm's attacks and movements as long as you have more Hit Dice than the swarm. Even when you aren't standing amid a swarm, your body crawls with vermin, and their chitinous bodies increase your natural armor bonus by +1. At 11th level, this bonus increases to +2, and at 17th level it increases to +3.</p>",
